  "name": "RPlog_Another_Late_Night_at_the_Casino",
  "title": "Another Late Night at the Casino",
  "summary": "At a casino, the smuggler captain Violet 'Allure' keeps company with the gruff, self-deprecating CSSD Chief Medical Officer Xar'on Tanner as he loses badly at the Lugjack slot machines while she wins. When Violet decides to cash out and return to her ship, she asks Xar'on to escort her to the starport, and he gallantly drapes his lab coat over her shoulders against the night chill. Along the way he grumbles about the upcoming starfighter competition and recounts a disastrous trip to Ord Mantell. Back aboard Violet's ship Venture, the two share fine black membrosia and easy conversation, during which Violet reveals she is a semi-retired CSA resource vice-prex stuck in a security post and warns the doctor against asking too many questions. The evening winds down warmly, and Xar'on gathers his bag and bids the captain goodnight.",
